    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the brioche is toasted, wipe the pan clean and return it to a medium heat</p><p>Add your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong> with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and cook for 1 min or until warmed through</p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>black sesame seeds</strong> over the chips – these are your <strong>black sesame chips</strong></p>",
