    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top your <strong>toasted brioche base </strong>with a <strong>pork patty</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>warmed hoisin sauce</strong>, some <strong>cucumber salad</strong>, <strong>spring onion strips</strong> and the <strong>brioche lid</strong></p><p>Serve any <strong>remaining cucumber salad </strong>and the<strong> black sesame chips </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
